data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News According to official news, BNB Chain will launch a Meme coin liquidity support plan, with the first round of support funds up to 4.4 million US dollars, starting on February 18, 2025, and the daily competition time is 8 am Beijing time to 8 am the next day (24 hours); the weekly competition time is 8 am on February 18, 2025 to 8 am on February 24, 2025 Beijing time.
The BSC Ecosystem Meme Coin participation requirements are:
·Issuing platforms: Four.meme, Burve, Gra.Fun, PinkSale, Flap, TokenFi, Beeper, HoloworldAI, Myshell.
·Meme coins must have been issued for at least 48 hours at the beginning of each competition;
The winning criteria are:
·Market value: The market value must reach US$1 million or more;
·Holding addresses: No less than 1,000;
·Token supply contribution: The project must add 10% of the token supply to the liquidity pool;
·Holding distribution: The top 10 externally owned accounts (eoa) must not hold more than 10% of the total supply, and holders are encouraged to manage assets through lock-up or linear release;
·The project must verify its token source code on bscscan or pass a security audit.
After confirming that the winner meets the requirements, BNB Chain will announce the winner's information on the X (Twitter) platform and complete liquidity support within 5 days.
It is reported that BNB Chain will focus on the top Memecoins on a daily and weekly basis, and directly inject BNB token liquidity from the BNB Chain Foundation wallet into the liquidity pool of the winning project. This liquidity will be permanently retained in the pool and will not be withdrawn. It is worth noting that this event is the first round of the BNB Chain Meme coin incentive plan, and more incentive plans will be launched in the future based on community user feedback.
